! write_box_fts

! PURPOSE

! Smooth the FTS spectra in input_file to output_file

! SYNTAX

! @ write_box_fts input_file output_file

! tell CLASS to be quiet
sic MESSAGE CLASS S=FE

set angle sec

say Smoothing &1 to file &2

file in &1

file out &2 single /overwrite

find /telescope 30M-F0*

! A) set rest frequency to 12CO(2-1)
! B) smooth FTS to 2.54km/s channels
@herapipe/class/loop_write.class 230538.000

